    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras/532a5fd67754acd21767371edda79866.avif?t=1762947281\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras_big/532a5fd67754acd21767371edda79866.avif?t=1762947281 width=800 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snails &amp; Potions is a fast paced party game, where you and one friend are tasked with getting your respective snail to the finish line. Forage items from around the map to brew potions. You can then use these potions to boost your snail, or perhaps sabotage your opponents snail. There are no rules, so employ whatever tactic you think will help you win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras/af95439480e89597f32c8962e65ac3ab.avif?t=1762947281\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras_big/af95439480e89597f32c8962e65ac3ab.avif?t=1762947281 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras/70e044c75afd85e1482ca19f5a30ef0c.avif?t=1762947281\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224810/extras_big/70e044c75afd85e1482ca19f5a30ef0c.avif?t=1762947281 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by a team of 5 students during the course &quot;Game Projects&quot; in the bachelor program Digital Arts and Entertainment at Hogeschool West-Vlaanderen in Belgium.</p>",
